table.name: item_value_set
table.description: This table contains the item values based on the Inventory Organization, Partner, Partner Site, Packaged Item, and Country of Origin.

columns.name: DOMAIN_NAME
columns.description: Database domain where this data is stored.

columns.name: INSERT_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data insert user.

columns.name: INSERT_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data insertion.

columns.name: UPDATE_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the user who updated the data.

columns.name: UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data update.

columns.name: ITEM_GID
columns.description: Identifies the item corresponding to the item value set.

columns.name: SEQ_NUMBER
columns.description: Sequence number of the item value set

columns.name: INVENTORY_ORGANIZATION_GID
columns.description: Identifies the inventory organization corresponding to the item value set.

columns.name: PARTNER_GID
columns.description: Identifies the partner corresponding to the item value set.

columns.name: PARTNER_SITE_GID
columns.description: Identifies the partner site corresponding to the item value set.

columns.name: PACKAGE_ITEM_GID
columns.description: Identifies the package item corresponding to the item value set.

columns.name: COUNTRY_OF_ORIGIN_GID
columns.description: Identifies the origin of the goods corresponding on the item value set.

columns.name: LOT_NUMBER
columns.description: Identifies the lot number corresponding on the item value set.

columns.name: SERIAL_NUMBER
columns.description: Identifies the sequence number corresponding on the item value set

columns.name: IDENTIFIER1
columns.description: Indicates the identifier corresponding on the item value set.

columns.name: IDENTIFIER2
columns.description: Indicates the identifier corresponding on the item value set.

columns.description: Indicates the identifier corresponding on the item value set.
